@startuml AD_configuration_current
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Activity Diagram: Configuration Flow (Current-State)

|User|
start
:Create campaign;
:Create project;

|Project Service|
:Persist project with status PENDING\nand config_status DRAFT;

|User|
:Create datasource;
:Create crawl targets;
:Adjust crawl mode if needed;

|Ingest Service|
:Persist datasource and targets;

|User|
if (Need crisis monitoring?) then (Yes)
  :Configure crisis rules;
  |Project Service|
  :Upsert crisis config;
endif

|User|
:Review readiness inputs;
stop
@enduml
